reviewText: like all Rin Tin Tin films but better quality of this film is from Grapevine  on a double feature.  Should be available from amazon or direct from Grapevine Video.  The second feature- "Death Goes North  has recently been released by Sony Pictures as a DVD-R but a good print.
our GSD made us buy it. she was disappointed because the jacket fooled her:  this video is NOT in color and is of poor quality. But then, a GSD is the hero so it can't be all bad...
